        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51409637/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51409637-1.jpg" alt="小雨红花" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35344410/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35344410/" class="">无上咒</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51409637/" class=" " title="小雨红花">小雨红花</a>
                (不念过去，不畏将来)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35344410">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">波飞太液心无往，云起魔崖梦欲腾。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-06-10 17:07</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                波飞太液心无往，云起魔崖梦欲腾。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35344410/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2015-06-10 17:07
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="35344373">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51409637/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51409637-1.jpg" alt="小雨红花" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35344373/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35344373/" class="">自欺 欺人 被人欺</a></h3>
          </div>
